reviewText:
Can't even make it to the game, it just loops at Would you like to link your Steam account to your Mber account? This is required if you bought your game via Steam." Pretty sure I bought a log-in simulator 2014. 0/10 for survival game. 11/10 for log-in simulation. Great release!

Edit: Managed to get past the log in screen ^^

@Sneeker I don't expect a game to be perfect on release but I expect a fully released game to not freeze at the server list for over 10 minutes
